	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The only thing worse would be a game where once enough characters on the cartridge get killed off, the player has to pay to revive characters. Someone seems to <a href="http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FinalDeath" class="postlink">think</a> that Hideo Kojima has suggested this mechanic in interviews; I just find it too arcade-like for a console environment.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
